No. 10-8486. William Clayton McKinnedy, III, Petitioner v. Cecil Reynolds, Warden, et al. 562 U.S. 1268, 131 S. Ct. 1615,

179 L. Ed. 2d 496,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1971. March 7, 2011.
